graph.math

Class CzekanovskiDiceDistance<V extends Vertex,E extends Edge<V>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • graph.math.CzekanovskiDiceDistance<V,E>

  • public class CzekanovskiDiceDistance<V extends Vertex,E extends Edge<V>>
extends java.lang.Object
    A class for calculating Czekanovski-Dice distances. With respect to Czekanovski-Dice distance, two vertices are close to each other if they have many common vertices.
    Author:
    Renata
